    <item>
      <title>欧洲的全球绿色愿景再次过于激进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/europe-s-global-green-ambitions-push-too-hard-once-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三年前，超过 100 位世界领导人在 COP26 气候大会上承诺扭转每年数百万公顷林地被毁的趋势，欧洲由此制定了遏制全球森林砍伐的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/europe-s-global-green-ambitions-push-too-hard-once-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡前部长因受贿被判入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/singapore-ex-minister-iswaran-sentenced-to-12-months-in-jail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡法院周四判处一名前部长入狱，这是半个世纪以来的第一次。新加坡试图发出明确信号，即不会容忍破坏其廉洁治理热情的行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/singapore-ex-minister-iswaran-sentenced-to-12-months-in-jail</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 02:41:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
